The game features 126 tracks in 16 sceneries and 19 cars.  Game modes
include: Single Race, Tutorials and Championships, Multiplayer, Split
Screen. Also Replays and Ghost drive are present.

The Track Editor allows modifying and creating tracks.  Both run on
Linux and Windows.

The game aims at a rally style of driving (like in Richard Burns Rally),
with possible stunt elements (loops, jumps).  It also introduces road
pipes, and provides a 3D spline generated road.
